You can easily remove the background content, by creating a custom implicit ModernDialog style that derives from the default ModernDialog style. In your custom style set the BackgroundContent property to null like so:<br />
<pre><code>&lt;Style TargetType=&quot;mui:ModernDialog&quot; BasedOn=&quot;{StaticResource {x:Type mui:ModernDialog}}&quot;&gt;
  &lt;Setter Property=&quot;BackgroundContent&quot; Value=&quot;{x:Null}&quot; /&gt;
&lt;/Style&gt;</code></pre>

For some additional information on deriving from implicit and default MUI styles, see <a href="https://mui.codeplex.com/wikipage?title=How%20to%20derive%20custom%20style%20from%20MUI%20style" rel="nofollow">this tutorial</a>.<br />
